{"tid":1301860,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"(精簡version)DSE/JUPAS放榜小提示","createTime":"2019-07-09T17:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T01:30:55.000Z","uid":248380,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a846b6405c4f453d5028c7029442916f44e6dc28","tid":1301860,"uid":248380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:56:42.000Z","msg":"坊間有好多假資訊<br />\n希望今次post做到一個護身符<br />\n俾大家求個安心<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">可以唔信個post<br />\n但千萬唔好信果啲電話hardsell嘅人<br />\n所謂講座係叫你俾錢報啲非本地學院課程<br />\n係EAPP入面未見過嘅學校<br />\n例如HKUX, UCHX, Cxmpxss cxllege, 林肯商XX等等</span><br />\n自己上網Search有關資訊<br />\n以前熱線三四年內已經接過不少電話問<br />\n通常放榜後就會打電話黎『關心』你<br />\n眼中其實只係為錢/佣金<br />\n真嘅放榜輔導組織<br />\n一般都係忙於聽電話(熱線義工經驗)<br />\n唔會得閒主動call人<br />\n更不可能hardsell人讀課程<br />\n冇咁多乜野隱世名校咁著數打電話益你<br />\n不要信0分都讀得/國際認可<br />\n係咁勁嘅學校就唔會電話hardsell你<br />\n<br />\nDSE放榜然後不足一個月就到JUPAS放榜<br />\nJUPAS放榜係8月5日上午9時正<br />\n前路滿希望果類陳腔濫調就唔多說<br />\n最直接同最有效方法講返重點<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">留意清楚各項Deadline！！！！！<br />\n不論Conditional offer, 留位費, JUPAS改選日子</span><br />\n<br />\n可以話忙但亦可以話唔忙<br />\nDSE放榜/JUPAS放榜要處理嘅事<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">A. 有冇需要appeal<br />\nB. 諗JUPAS改選<br />\nC. 確認confidential offer<br />\nD. 親身現場去報自資院校Degree/asso/hd/基礎文憑<br />\nE. 確認JUPAS offer<br />\nF. 交留位費/學費</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">做嘅野不外乎四樣：<br />\n試唔試Appeal<br />\n諗讀咩<br />\n去報咩<br />\n確認</span><br />\n<br />\n簡單物件List：<br />\n(要親身去報院校的話)<br />\na. 適量現金(報課程預一間要～$300報名費)<br />\nb. 八達通(搭車，同要知去邊)<br />\nc. 中四至中六校內成績表正副本&amp;SLP<br />\nd. DSE成績正本加影印本<br />\ne. 相片數張(學生相, 即係日常用果種相)<br />\nf.&nbsp; 放榜指南(學校應該會派，我會放ebook version)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.student.hk/site/?q=e_book/1484/3352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.student.hk%2Fsite%2F%3Fq%3De_book%2F1484%2F3352&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBPZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=c2030c06\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.student.hk/site/?q=e_book/1484/3352</a><br />\ng. 衫褲(唔想著住校服Interview就拎後備衫褲/先返屋企換)<br />\n<br />\n主要選擇方向<br />\na. JUPAS課程<br />\nb. 自資院校degree<br />\nc. Asso/HD<br />\nd. 基礎文憑/毅進<br />\ne. 日校Repeat/自修retake<br />\nf. 就業/職業導向課程<br />\ng. 一邊讀課程一邊retake DSE<br />\n<br />\n自己可能同屋企人傾下<br />\n自己想清楚方向<br />\n雖然都有可能會後悔/改變主意<br />\n盡量不要令自己後悔<br />\n冇話好定唔好<br />\n每人有不同興趣不同選擇<br />\n唔好信asso一定後門入到u<br />\n亦唔好信DSE下年retake一定高分<br />\n讓乜乜悔終生亦都係<br />\n要做決定同最後負責的人只有自己<br />\n自己要衡量自己情況而決定<br />\n<br />\n多人係自資Degree/Asso/HD/水泡科/retake/repeat中比較<br />\n但好難講邊個一定較好<br />\n要視乎每人實際情況而定<br />\n每人有唔同選擇<br />\n可以同老師傾下<br />\n有需要可以打去各放榜熱線同人傾下<br />\n雙向交流好過單方面文字<br />\n<br />\nDSE&gt;20 較大機會入JUPAS各大學<br />\nDSE&gt;15 有機會入JUPAS SSSDP課程<br />\n另外仲有JUPAS補選<br />\n課程太多而且每人Target不同唔講太多<br />\n都要睇自己嘅選擇<br />\n想唔想讀果樣野都好重要<br />\n放榜指南入面有好多課程睇<br />\n需要softcopy睇返上面條link<br />\n時間關係打多次link<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.student.hk/site/?q=e_book/1484/3352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.student.hk%2Fsite%2F%3Fq%3De_book%2F1484%2F3352&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBPZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=c2030c06\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.student.hk/site/?q=e_book/1484/3352</a><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n1. 7月10號放榜及之後兩三日<br />\n學校考生係返自己學校拎DSE成績<br />\n至於幾點就睇返自己學校安排<br />\n通常都要你地著校服返學校<br />\n睇完成績後就開始要決定點做<br />\nA. 諗JUPAS改選<br />\nB. 確認EAPP confidential offer<br />\nC. 親身現場去報自資院校Degree/asso/hd/基礎文憑<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n如果之前係EAPP報咗名有condition offer<br />\n想讀而又meet到requirement<br />\n可以跟指示去確認返offer<br />\nJUPAS改選日子同時段<br />\n每人都會有唔同<br />\n老師可能都會同你地講<br />\n一般係JUPAS放榜後三日內<br />\n今年係星期四至六<br />\n留意返自己時段<br />\n有Interview嘅科可能就要放返前<br />\n就大dd機會入到<br />\n詳情要睇返佢Interview有無寫例如只in Band A<br />\n<br />\n2. JUPAS排序<br />\nJUPAS係跟成績排位<br />\n但排序亦都需要理會<br />\n睇下過往收分嘅UQ, mean同LQ<br />\n高過UQ係幾安全但低過LQ就機會微<br />\n不過都要睇實際情況例如幾多位<br />\n搏唔搏同有幾搏都係自己揀<br />\n唔好後悔就得<br />\n留意有冇Interview<br />\ninterview有冇限band A<br />\n有收到interview就努力爭取表現<br />\n然後就等8月5號上午9時放榜結果<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n要講的話真係太多字<br />\n我上面貼嘅放榜指南都夠基本應對<br />\nAppeal, 院校資料等都已經包括<br />\n真係唔打太長<br />\n有人問到我再答la<br />\n祝大家好運<br />\n真係有需要再留言問<br />\n或者ig, tg(同名)詳細問<br />\n時間ok下盡量答到都答嘅<br />\n唔好問我有咩課程推介<br />\n開post只係幫下人<br />\n冇任何野可以sell亦冇野可以宣傳<br />\n係你自己決定要讀啲咩<br />\n每人有唔同興趣<br />\n只要有心嘅話依家開始努力都唔怕<br />\nDSE分數的確唔係等於所有<br />\n搵自己方向更加重要<br />\n重點係唔好讀咗果啲冇認可嘅課程<br />\n讀咗就真係麻煩啲&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n未訓又等緊放榜嘅人早啲訓la<br />\n朝早養足精神<br />\n加油💪💪💪💪💪💪💪💪💪💪"},{"pid":"e1957fb4a6c858c6fa6819ee77b14066d0d11f8a","tid":1301860,"uid":210165,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:04:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"756e632b95dacab126a105194d98165129c4dfb8","tid":1301860,"uid":42374,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e1957fb4a6c858c6fa6819ee77b14066d0d11f8a","tid":1301860,"uid":210165,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:04:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:09:47.000Z","msg":"如果讀大學係為咗發達咁你都幾膚淺"},{"pid":"533f9fc42047f6b128c0f405751c93f5c98071a9","tid":1301860,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:12:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9258ab7ec45a9ffb59591ebcb8514e1c388e7dfd","tid":1301860,"uid":167499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:13:27.000Z","msg":"個位數分有咩讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca432ef4f052135afcec1e7f2c1d034ea1bb79f4","tid":1301860,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:15:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3df02f3d766c86a7d5ed921bea427702c98ca1f3","tid":1301860,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca432ef4f052135afcec1e7f2c1d034ea1bb79f4","tid":1301860,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9258ab7ec45a9ffb59591ebcb8514e1c388e7dfd","tid":1301860,"uid":167499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:13:27.000Z","msg":"個位數分有咩讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:15:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:16:59.000Z","msg":"有人唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25732a01b5624428869828db2b848d039801f0f","tid":1301860,"uid":42374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"533f9fc42047f6b128c0f405751c93f5c98071a9","tid":1301860,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"756e632b95dacab126a105194d98165129c4dfb8","tid":1301860,"uid":42374,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e1957fb4a6c858c6fa6819ee77b14066d0d11f8a","tid":1301860,"uid":210165,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:04:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:09:47.000Z","msg":"如果讀大學係為咗發達咁你都幾膚淺"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:12:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:17:08.000Z","msg":"愈讀得多就愈覺得自己無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n生命只有一次機會 認識多啲世界你話幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人死咗又帶唔走錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大學有咁多機遇俾你去嘗試<br />\n識人又好 發展興趣又好 exchange又好 住hall拍拖又好 認識多啲自己又好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b544882ce608553cf06b65949c8202a45b7006","tid":1301860,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3df02f3d766c86a7d5ed921bea427702c98ca1f3","tid":1301860,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca432ef4f052135afcec1e7f2c1d034ea1bb79f4","tid":1301860,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9258ab7ec45a9ffb59591ebcb8514e1c388e7dfd","tid":1301860,"uid":167499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:13:27.000Z","msg":"個位數分有咩讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:15:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:16:59.000Z","msg":"有人唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:18:12.000Z","msg":"讀完yijin邊個話一定要做狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba5c044bf7f167c1ed098dae875240e37a6c236","tid":1301860,"uid":167499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ca432ef4f052135afcec1e7f2c1d034ea1bb79f4","tid":1301860,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9258ab7ec45a9ffb59591ebcb8514e1c388e7dfd","tid":1301860,"uid":167499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:13:27.000Z","msg":"個位數分有咩讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:15:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:20:08.000Z","msg":"自修生讀完中四冇讀未夠21<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c845c7bc2bdcb4dce80eb364667372e28fe9992","tid":1301860,"uid":248380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"533f9fc42047f6b128c0f405751c93f5c98071a9","tid":1301860,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"756e632b95dacab126a105194d98165129c4dfb8","tid":1301860,"uid":42374,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e1957fb4a6c858c6fa6819ee77b14066d0d11f8a","tid":1301860,"uid":210165,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:04:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:09:47.000Z","msg":"如果讀大學係為咗發達咁你都幾膚淺"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:12:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:42:21.000Z","msg":"你id同你講嘅野都幾唔match👀<br />\n咁每人有唔同需要<br />\n可能有人想早啲做野<br />\n我唔會話讀書係must<br />\n做野會有做野好處<br />\n但亦有人真係想讀書同真係需要讀書<br />\n<br />\n人際/圈子同增廣見聞係會有<br />\n但思維, 知識同技能<br />\n真係可能讀書先能得到<br />\n<br />\n或者有人覺得讀書唔重要<br />\n讀書其實唔係真係讀一本書<br />\n讀書係一個學習知識過程嘅簡稱<br />\n唔係所有野實踐就可以<br />\n最明顯係科技<br />\n唔會拎d金屬搵火燒下就整到部電腦出黎<br />\n你住家用緊嘅電話亦都係<br />\n你應該唔會覺得你依家用緊果部智能電話係隨機組合而形成<br />\n唔讀過相關嘅野都唔會整得到<br />\n依啲知識都係由學習所得到(讀書)<br />\n有啲野中六讀完書出嚟真係做唔到<br />\n亂整會爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算真係自學去學寫電話app<br />\n自學依個過程其實都係「讀書」<br />\n<br />\n可能有啲工作真係唔駛點讀書<br />\n但有啲工作的確需要學歷/技能<br />\n如果冇人讀書嘅話<br />\n科技野都唔存在<br />\n醫學都係建基於「讀書」<br />\n而且仲要讀好耐<br />\n未必每個人會選擇「讀書」<br />\n亦唔一定係對個個人都好有用<br />\n但真係唔能夠否定「讀書」作用"},{"pid":"58626b2a2da124b99fe33a10e8499e41013b4ccd","tid":1301860,"uid":214482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1957fb4a6c858c6fa6819ee77b14066d0d11f8a","tid":1301860,"uid":210165,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:04:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:46:39.000Z","msg":"讀書出黎選擇唔多，唔讀書選擇更少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3480c33f04e622d9e879fb56764c21ed2bf1256","tid":1301860,"uid":214482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3zJBpZ9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3zJBpZ9.png&h=a0f83e92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報讀非本地高等及專業教育課程前，注意該課程是否經已辦理註冊或豁免註冊及相應的資歷架構級別。切勿一次繳交全部學費。要索取並保留學費收據。如有疑問，請到教育局網站查詢。<br />\n<a href=\"https://applications.edb.gov.hk/ncr/ncr.aspx?langno=2&amp;searchtype=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapplications.edb.gov.hk%2Fncr%2Fncr.aspx%3Flangno%3D2%26searchtype%3D3&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBPZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=660a73a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://applications.edb.gov.hk/ncr/ncr.aspx?langno=2&amp;searchtype=3</a><br />\n<br />\n教育局關心您。"},{"pid":"17c93bf38be17697d9cec7c66332e53e27823859","tid":1301860,"uid":248380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ba5c044bf7f167c1ed098dae875240e37a6c236","tid":1301860,"uid":167499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ca432ef4f052135afcec1e7f2c1d034ea1bb79f4","tid":1301860,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9258ab7ec45a9ffb59591ebcb8514e1c388e7dfd","tid":1301860,"uid":167499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:13:27.000Z","msg":"個位數分有咩讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:15:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:20:08.000Z","msg":"自修生讀完中四冇讀未夠21<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:59:48.000Z","msg":"依類case就會比較麻煩<br />\n一般VTC基礎文憑同毅進都要中六學歷/21歲<br />\nDSE分數就取代唔到中六學歷<br />\n所以條件上睇依刻係報唔到依兩樣<br />\n<br />\nVTC會有職專文憑/職專文憑/文憑比中三離校生<br />\n不過幾專同可能要讀三年<br />\n要睇下有冇你興趣同想講嘅野<br />\n其他學校都有部份有文憑課程讀<br />\n有部份唔駛中六學歷<br />\n但可能要例如DSE五科達6分(中英文要1)<br />\n你可以睇下符唔符合到<br />\n下面係學友社放榜指南2019第二冊相關部份<br />\n詳細你可以再係睇下 <a href=\"http://www.student.hk/site/?q=system/files/BK2_05.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.student.hk%2Fsite%2F%3Fq%3Dsystem%2Ffiles%2FBK2_05.pdf&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBPZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=fab3fd2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.student.hk/site/?q=system/files/BK2_05.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n聽朝先放榜<br />\n如果你DSE成績只係差少少<br />\n亦可以考慮努力下年再retake DSE"},{"pid":"4a9279f02faa9a53a6bc7c895daa8b45c9294845","tid":1301860,"uid":167499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17c93bf38be17697d9cec7c66332e53e27823859","tid":1301860,"uid":248380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ba5c044bf7f167c1ed098dae875240e37a6c236","tid":1301860,"uid":167499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ca432ef4f052135afcec1e7f2c1d034ea1bb79f4","tid":1301860,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:15:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:20:08.000Z","msg":"自修生讀完中四冇讀未夠21<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:59:48.000Z","msg":"依類case就會比較麻煩<br />\n一般VTC基礎文憑同毅進都要中六學歷/21歲<br />\nDSE分數就取代唔到中六學歷<br />\n所以條件上睇依刻係報唔到依兩樣<br />\n<br />\nVTC會有職專文憑/職專文憑/文憑比中三離校生<br />\n不過幾專同可能要讀三年<br />\n要睇下有冇你興趣同想講嘅野<br />\n其他學校都有部份有文憑課程讀<br />\n有部份唔駛中六學歷<br />\n但可能要例如DSE五科達6分(中英文要1)<br />\n你可以睇下符唔符合到<br />\n下面係學友社放榜指南2019第二冊相關部份<br />\n詳細你可以再係睇下 <a href=\"http://www.student.hk/site/?q=system/files/BK2_05.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.student.hk%2Fsite%2F%3Fq%3Dsystem%2Ffiles%2FBK2_05.pdf&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBPZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=fab3fd2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.student.hk/site/?q=system/files/BK2_05.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n聽朝先放榜<br />\n如果你DSE成績只係差少少<br />\n亦可以考慮努力下年再retake DSE"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:30:55.000Z","msg":"6分 好彩中英都有1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}